metadata.name: Contributor of Chapter One
metadata.description: [Legends of the FirstBorne](https://thefirstborne.wtf) is a community driven novel where NFT holders contribute ideas and vote on the direction the story takes. The novel is funded by a collection of 11,111 unique NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. [Embark on the journey with us...](https://discord.gg/SsJ9978UgB)
